<title>USA: StorMedia named in suit filed by Maxtor.</title>
<headline>StorMedia named in suit filed by Maxtor.</headline>
<dateline>LONGMONT, Colo. 1996-12-19</dateline>
<text>
<p>Maxtor Corp said late Thursday that it filed a lawsuit in Boulder County District Court in Colorado against StorMedia Inc, claiming actual damages of more than $100 million and punitive damages.</p>
<p>The company said the lawsuit alleges breach of contract, negligent misrepresentation and breaches of warranties.</p>
<p>A spokesman for StorMedia declined comment on the lawsuit.</p>
